WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.760
Hi, my name is Brendan Cullen and I'm a Data Science Educator at Posit.

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:17.400
I work with a team of fellow educators who specialize in teaching open source, code-first

00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:23.559
data science, and we are really excited to be offering a workshop at PositConf this year,

00:00:23.559 --> 00:00:28.799
Introduction to Data Science with R. In this video, we'll share with you a few reasons

00:00:28.799 --> 00:00:32.160
why we think you should join us.

00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:37.240
The attractive thing about this workshop is that it is a Posit Academy course.

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:42.119
That means you'll learn by doing a six-week online apprenticeship with a Posit mentor

00:00:42.119 --> 00:00:43.119
and several co-apprentices.

00:00:43.119 --> 00:00:49.680
You'll meet as a group twice a week to work through a realistic project and to get feedback

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:51.279
on your work.

00:00:51.279 --> 00:00:55.720
At the first meeting each week, you'll have a chance to just work together and ask questions

00:00:55.720 --> 00:00:58.200
with your mentor and your fellow students.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:02.400
At the second meeting, you'll present your work to everyone else.

00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:06.040
This meeting is not optional, but it's the place where you'll get the personalized

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:09.959
feedback that will help you become a better data scientist.

00:01:09.959 --> 00:01:13.559
In between the meetings, we'll give you interactive tutorials that you can complete

00:01:13.559 --> 00:01:17.360
to learn the materials for next week's part of the project.

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:21.400
As the project draws to an end, it'll be time for conference.

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:25.559
We'll see you there in person during the workshop days and we'll finish up the project

00:01:25.559 --> 00:01:26.559
together.

00:01:26.559 --> 00:01:27.440
I hope to see you there.

00:01:28.440 --> 00:01:34.320
Hi, I'm Sisa Madhikari and I'm one of the content writers here at Academy.

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:38.120
Learning with Academy is both fun and effective.

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:42.160
Because the courses are spread over a couple of weeks, you never feel like you're drinking

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:43.160
from a firehose.

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:49.559
You have time to truly understand a concept before moving on to the next, but it is more

00:01:49.559 --> 00:01:52.760
social than a purely online course.

00:01:52.760 --> 00:01:58.160
You get to meet the same small group of students and mentor each week, so it's a more fun

00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.760
and supportive way of learning.

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:06.279
I want to share one final reason why you should join us for this Posit Academy workshop if

00:02:06.279 --> 00:02:08.360
you're interested in learning R.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:12.440
And that is, quite simply, that it works.

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:18.759
We've had great success training hundreds of data scientists, analysts, and researchers

00:02:18.759 --> 00:02:22.960
to learn R and to apply it to their daily work.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:28.440
With Academy, we've developed an evidence-based method for teaching the tidyverse that focuses

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:34.039
on building skills and not only learning facts.

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:41.119
Our approach involves repeated practice and in-depth feedback, which together form a solid

00:02:41.119 --> 00:02:44.720
mastery of R that lasts.

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:50.360
So we hope you'll join us and we look forward to seeing you online and in Chicago this September.

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:54.960
www.positacademy.org

